hen the center of $\\mathfrak{R}$ is $\\mathfrak{C}[\\Omega]$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 08:20:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Dec 2017 18:25:28 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 15 Mar 2020 03:24:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-17"}
