hosting orbital companions. In particular, tidally driven dynamos may\nexplain the observed magnetism of tidally deformed and rapidly rotating\nVega-like stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Nov 2017 10:33:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Jan 2018 09:54:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-01-24"}
